    <summary><span data-ttu-id="f9b3c-101"><see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter" /> コントロールでサイズを変更する行または列を指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b3c-101">Specifies the rows or columns that are resized by a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter" /> control.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  

<span data-ttu-id="f9b3c-102">この列挙体は、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeBehavior%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> プロパティの値を設定するために使用されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b3c-102">This enumeration is used to set the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeBehavior%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.</span></span>  

<span data-ttu-id="f9b3c-103">`BasedOnAlignment` 列挙値を使用した <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeBehavior%2A> プロパティの動作は、次のように決定されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b3c-103">The behavior of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeBehavior%2A> property with the `BasedOnAlignment` enumeration value is determined as follows:</span></span>  

- <span data-ttu-id="f9b3c-104"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeDirection%2A> プロパティの値によって領域が行間で再配分されることが指定されている場合、再配布は次のガイドラインに従います。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b3c-104">If the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeDirection%2A> property specifies that space is redistributed between rows, the redistribution follows these guidelines:</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="f9b3c-105"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> プロパティが <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Top?displayProperty=nameWithType>に設定されている場合、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> に指定された行とその行の上にある行の間に領域が再配分されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b3c-105">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Top?displayProperty=nameWithType>, space is redistributed between the row that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> and the row that is above that row.</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="f9b3c-106"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> プロパティが <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Bottom?displayProperty=nameWithType>に設定されている場合、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> に指定された行とその行の下にある行の間に領域が再配分されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b3c-106">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Bottom?displayProperty=nameWithType>, space is redistributed between the row that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> and the row that is below that row.</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="f9b3c-107"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> プロパティが <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Center?displayProperty=nameWithType>に設定されている場合は、上の行と <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>に指定されている行の下にある行の間の領域が再配分されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b3c-107">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Center?displayProperty=nameWithType>, space is redistributed between the row that is above and the row that is below the row that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>.</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="f9b3c-108"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> プロパティが <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType>に設定されている場合は、上の行と <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>に指定されている行の下にある行の間の領域が再配分されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b3c-108">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType>, space is redistributed between the row that is above and the row that is below the row that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>.</span></span>  
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f9b3c-109"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeDirection%2A> プロパティの値によって領域が列間で再配分されることが指定されている場合、再配布は次のガイドラインに従います。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b3c-109">If the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeDirection%2A> property specifies that space is redistributed between columns, the redistribution follows these guidelines:</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="f9b3c-110"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> プロパティが <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Left?displayProperty=nameWithType>に設定されている場合、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> に指定されている列と左側の列の間に領域が再配分されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b3c-110">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Left?displayProperty=nameWithType>, space is redistributed between the column that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> and the column that is to the left.</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="f9b3c-111"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> プロパティが <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Right?displayProperty=nameWithType>に設定されている場合、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> に指定されている列と右側の列の間に領域が再配分されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b3c-111">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Right?displayProperty=nameWithType>, space is redistributed between the column that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> and the column that is to the right.</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="f9b3c-112"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> プロパティが <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Center?displayProperty=nameWithType>に設定されている場合、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>に指定されている列の左右の列の間に領域が再配分されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b3c-112">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Center?displayProperty=nameWithType>, space is redistributed between the columns that are to the left and right of the column that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>.</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="f9b3c-113"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> プロパティが <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType>に設定されている場合、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>に指定されている列の左右の列の間に領域が再配分されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b3c-113">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType>, space is redistributed between the columns that are to the left and right of the column that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
